# Backend Docker build context allowlist.
# Keep production image builds deterministic and avoid copying local caches,
# datasets, frontend assets, virtualenvs, logs, uploads, and secret files.

*

!app/
!app/**/
!app/**/*.py
!app/**/*.yaml
!app/**/*.yml
!app/**/README.md
!main.py
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!README.md
!Dockerfile
!docker-entrypoint.sh
!.dockerignore
